    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没事，我们回去吧。任务简报……还没做完呢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，我……我想求你帮忙。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虽然瑟瑞斯一直都是很认真的性格，但由于记忆缺陷的困扰，平日里的她总会在那份认真之余还留有一丝困惑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而此刻我眼前的瑟瑞斯眼中却没有那份困惑，取而代之的是坚决，以及……一点点愤怒？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我怀疑我的记忆被改动过！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "出发之前我就觉得不对劲了。那天……就是想去找你说这件事。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你可以直接推门进去的，为什么要躲在门外呢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "因为……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "因为我……！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的表情让我想到了一种可能性。虽然很荒谬，但我决定试着问出口。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-2",
        "Flag": "b-2",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "b-2-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你在怀疑苔丝，对吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我怀疑她和改动我记忆的那些人是一伙的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "的确是荒谬的发言。不过这或许能解开一个一直横在我心里的疑问。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "苔丝的真实身份到底是什么，或许能从瑟瑞斯即将说出口的事情里窥见一些端倪。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-3",
        "Flag": "b-3",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "b-3-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "安抚瑟瑞斯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "来，先坐下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "小心些，别让碎玻璃扎着了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她站着不肯动，我不得不费了些力气才让她放弃执拗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "等她终于在我对面老老实实坐好之后，我把目光移向了她手里紧紧攥着的那个东西。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你说你怀疑苔丝和改动你记忆的人是一伙的，也就意味着你大概知道是什么人改动了你的记忆？",
        "disable": 0
    },
