    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而且从那之后，我也总觉得自己很容易把事情记错，或者记混。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就像这样！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她拿起录音笔，低头检查着录音文件，然后播放了其中一段。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 2,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员？这个时间了你来这里做什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
